==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Setbolt
<hw>Set"bolt`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Shipbuilding)</fld>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>An iron pin, or bolt, for fitting planks closely
together.</def> <rj><au>Craig.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A bolt used for forcing another bolt out of its
hole.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Set chisel</ent>⟦br⟧
